                "game-id": "05fb73ab58056899aa7995643a0d42a0",
                "text": "A creature with this trait is a member of the tripkee ancestry. Tripkees are a family of froglike humanoids. An ability with this trait can be used or selected only by tripkees. An item with this trait is created and used by tripkees.",
